<td colspan="2">Elliot,<br />
<br />
This is <em>so</em> poorly written; it reads like a Deerie still wet behind the ears slapped it together. Seriously, what were you trying to do here, Elliot? Stick to the fucking format.<br />
<br />
I know you and your team are still hung up over Charles and what he did, but I think you should take a break. This whole ordeal has been affecting your work habits and mental health. We're all worried about how paranoid you're being about SAPPHIRE. I'm forwarding you HR's email address so that you may seek some PTO.<br />
